'''Arnie Jorgensen''' is an American comic book artist and video game concept artist.

Jorgenson worked for [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC Comics]], [[Wikipedia:Malibu Comics|Malibu Comics]] and [[Marvel Comics]]. He later became a concept artist in the video game industry, working for companies like [[Wikipedia:Ion Storm Inc.|Ion Storm]] and [[Wikipedia:Retro Studios|Retro Studios]] before he became Senior Concept Artist of [[Sony|Sony Online Entertainment's]] MMORPG ''[[Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided]]'' and its three expansions.

